&lt;h2 id=&#34;Choose-a-Programming-Language&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Choose-a-Programming-Language&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Choose a Programming Language&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Choose a Programming Language&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Youâ€™ll need to choose a programming language for the coding interviews you do,&lt;br&gt;but youâ€™ll also need to find a language that you can use to study computer science concepts.&lt;/p&gt;
