&lt;h2 id=&#34;I-O-Device-Features&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#I-O-Device-Features&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;I&amp;#x2F;O Device Features&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;I&amp;#x2F;O Device Features&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
